frontMatter.mdxContent:
---
title: Chakra UI Data Tables - Horizon UI
description: Renders controllable data tables in React.
---

Check out our React datatables examples and learn how to add advanced
interaction controls to your tables the easy way.

## Usage

```jsx
function Example() {
  return (
    <Box bg="red.400" color="white">
      <iframe
        src="https://codesandbox.io/embed/nice-water-1v4hzb?fontsize=14&hidenavigation=1&initialpath=%2Fdata-tables&module=%2Fsrc%2Fcomponents%2FdataTables.js&theme=dark"
        width="100%"
        height="500px"
        ms="-15px"
        overflow="hidden"
      ></iframe>
    </Box>
  )
}
```

```tsx
<TableTopCreators
  tableData={tableDataTopCreators}
  columnsData={tableColumnsTopCreators}
/>
```

## Table data example

```tsx
const tableColumnsTopCreators = [
  {
    Header: "Name",
    accessor: "name",
  },
  {
    Header: "Artworks",
    accessor: "artworks",
  },
  {
    Header: "Rating",
    accessor: "rating",
  },
]
```

